Hyderabad-based business school, Siva Sivani Institute of Management, will organise a seminar on ‘Making an International Career and Changing Job Scenario’ at Karnataka Arts, Science and Commerce College on Friday at 10 a.m. Chari V.G., and P. Ranga Reddy, former RGM, The Hindu, Hyderabad, will speak.Final-year degree students, graduates of various disciplines and others interested in MBA courses, or those wanting to learn about international programs can participate. Entry is free, said a release.